{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":61984,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有些人不习惯自由","timestamp":1593409203,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61990,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 谁？","timestamp":1593409229,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":61998,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有些人认为自己的观念就该束缚一切跟他不同的人。","timestamp":1593409264,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62006,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有些人认为“人是万物的尺度”中的“人”指的是自己，有些人认为“人民的意志”中“人民”指的也是自己","timestamp":1593409304,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62027,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"有些人认为自己代表了所谓“大多数”人的意志 并认为“大多数”人可以强奸“少数”人","timestamp":1593409423,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62054,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"老八来也，你们可不要嫌恶心嗷","timestamp":1593409639,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62067,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 你又来了？祖安话用上还辩不过别人的那个？","timestamp":1593409761,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":62164,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":10608,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: ？","timestamp":1593410716,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":10608,"reply":8,"tag":null,"text":"## 在树洞做什么\n\n在树洞，没有什么非要做的事情，也没有什么不能做的事情。\n\n只要敲下几行文字，树洞可以满足你任何的交流需求：找到小众爱好的朋友，寻求学业发展的建议，交流对于社会问题的看法，在深夜倾诉内心的不安……是的，这看上去和任何一个社交软件没有区别，但请记住，在这里你的一切言行将不会被judge，而你的交流对象都是和你思维高度同频的T大同学。\n\n同样，出于对用户的尊重，我们不会给予过多应用方面的建议，在不越过某些红线的前提下，树洞的玩法完全由每一个人自己决定。在这里，匿名性保证了你可以放心吐露真实想法，而不用惧怕外人的眼光；校园性降低了交流壁垒，你可以随便玩校园小众的烂梗，而不用在乎外人尴尬的迷茫。\n\n原贴 #118","timestamp":1593409169,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782587,"url":"","vote":{}}}